<subSubSection id="F5ABDBA1ADA272F3600DF43B75B56FFB" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="C3CE59DF60D29ACA17A17C013EA4C00A" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">
<pageBreakToken id="B658292A4C239AF75790266A42491908" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" start="start">Diagnosis</pageBreakToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D03A84A874C28A731190F6334939FB96" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">
The new species is closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="88E2E7EF90807D29EA779C5D00805529" genus="C." lsidName="C. dolichocarpa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="dolichocarpa">
<emphasis id="3B750F0DF790804A25E942733942245B" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. dolichocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="D5B83B10AC100D41D85406249D99255B" genus="C." lsidName="C. longifructosa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="longifructosa">
<emphasis id="E827CE6C5CB66934CC1C29E99B56DD29" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. longifructosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Fig. 
<figureCitation id="F9EF5FD2B523EA575DBB60B3792762BC" captionStart="Figure 8" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figure 8. Cyrtandra longifructosa M. A. Johnson and closest relative (C. dolichocarpa) based on molecular phylogeny by Johnson et al. (2017). A C. longifructosa corolla, anterior view B C. longifructosa flower, lateral view C C. longifructosa elongate cylindrical fruits D C. longifructosa axillary inflorescence and young fruits E C. longifructosa shrub habit F C. dolichocarpa corolla, anterior view G C. dolichocarpa flower, lateral view H C. dolichocarpa shrub habit. All photos taken in the field by M. Johnson, with photos of C. longifructosa taken from the type collection." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.91.21623.figure8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/174661" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">8</figureCitation>
), but differs in its dense bristly pubescence on the young stems, leaves, petioles, and inflorescences (vs. moderate appressed pubescence on 
<taxonomicName id="C5AFF2E5424D2822A7AB847E12593647" genus="C." lsidName="C. dolichocarpa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="dolichocarpa">
<emphasis id="98073660861CAAF163A774D8CD0E533F" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. dolichocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; vs. glabrous on 
<taxonomicName id="772C3B949C2BB352F71AFD3E81B85294" genus="C." lsidName="C. longifructosa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="longifructosa">
<emphasis id="47305D349E56369AA103E8EC1EED0FFD" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. longifructosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), cauliflorous inflorescences (vs. axillary inflorescences in both 
<taxonomicName id="E076E010A9457E7123C695223BAB5676" genus="C." lsidName="C. dolichocarpa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="dolichocarpa">
<emphasis id="9971E567670E7576CD6F54A9D7D3AB3E" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. dolichocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="E363300F9D15DE1A244422C9FFE3E73E" genus="C." lsidName="C. longifructosa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="longifructosa">
<emphasis id="BA1AB6A473B6AAF775BC061C45902825" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. longifructosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), persistent foliaceous ovate white bracts to 10 mm long (vs. non-foliaceous green bracts to 5 mm long in 
<taxonomicName id="C304507B2900165637007DBEE638D9F4" genus="C." lsidName="C. dolichocarpa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="dolichocarpa">
<emphasis id="80BCD6AC105FE71EAED44DFB0CC4D749" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. dolichocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; vs. deciduous non-foliaceous lanceolate green bracts to 8 mm long in 
<taxonomicName id="F00FB3FBCB162F37C3CCB5A797867799" genus="C." lsidName="C. longifructosa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="longifructosa">
<emphasis id="295AC2A3C23D89D7DF0CE392EF8A75B2" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. longifructosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), and multiple persistent foliaceous white bracteoles (vs. single deciduous non-foliaceous green bracteoles in 
<taxonomicName id="F656A07DA5D51E6F6E79266A9F93665C" genus="C." lsidName="C. dolichocarpa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="dolichocarpa">
<emphasis id="0DA0355B312A7B4E987A85AF8D1050CF" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. dolichocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; vs. bracteoles absent in 
<taxonomicName id="0B3641BE60EAC5EDDA60E95B57EEB7D4" genus="C." lsidName="C. longifructosa" pageId="11" pageNumber="96" rank="species" species="longifructosa">
<emphasis id="DF0FDA9CFA29994F044158879A40EF72" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="96">C. longifructosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
